I finally have all my Jack Ryan movies in one set.  I am amazed how four different actors manged to capture an play the essence of Jack Ryan the CIA analyst with such continuity over a twenty four year span in time. Of the five films, my two favorites are The Hunt For Red October and Patriot Games; however, I give each or them a five star rating!
